OL,3,CWelsh devolution at 25: Reflecting on
OL,4,C25 years since the first Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FMonday 6 May marks 25 years since the
OL,8,Ffirst election to the in 1999.
OL,10,FIt followed a historic referendum in
OL,11,FSeptember 1997, which saw a narrow
OL,12,Fmajority back the creation of a
OL,13,Fdevolved government in Wales.
OL,15,F50.3% voted in for the creation of a
OL,16,FNational Assembly for Wales, as it was
OL,17,Fcalled when it was first established,
OL,18,Fwhich would transfer certain powers
OL,19,Ffrom Westminster to Wales.
