OL,3,CWelsh devolution at 25: Reflecting on
OL,4,C25 years since the first Senedd
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FFor instance, the Welsh electorate
OL,8,Fvoted in another devolution referendum
OL,9,Fin 2011, with 63.5% of voters backing
OL,10,Fthe idea the Senedd should be given
OL,11,Ffull primary law-making powers.
OL,13,FThe Senedd was then given reserved
OL,14,Fpowers in 2017.
OL,16,FAmong the new powers Wales' devolved
OL,17,Flegislature had responsibility for was
OL,18,Fthe power to decide its own name and
OL,19,Fthe voting system by which its Members
OL,20,Fare elected.
