OL,7,FNot all of the UK's devolved
OL,8,Fparliaments are the same, though.
OL,10,FWhilst Welsh justice and policing
OL,11,Fremain under the control of
OL,12,FWestminster, the Scottish Government
OL,13,Fdetermines those areas for itself. The
OL,14,Fsame is true for the Northern Ireland
OL,15,FAssembly, .
OL,17,FLike their counterparts in Edinburgh
OL,18,Fand Belfast, politicians in have
OL,19,Fpowers over key public services such
OL,20,Fas health and education.
